727899f-a.title: Queens: Rockaway Boulevard - 134th Avenue
727899f-a.text:
Rockaway Boulevard, east side, between One Hundred Thirty-
fourth and One Hundred Thirty-seventh Aves., showing the Abraham
Van Siclen residence. Another probable owner was W. Ingalls from
1860-1873.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

727898f-a.title: Queens: Rockaway Boulevard - 134th Avenue
727898f-a.text:
Rockaway Boulevard, east side, between One Hundred Thirty-fourth
and One Hundred Thirty-seventh Aves., showing the Isaac Snediker
house, which does not appear in the 1931 Queens Atlas.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
